reviewText: The best seasons of Carlos Mencia was 1 and 2,  after not making a season 5 and taking a break,  I find that carlos mencia has come back with a Kick @$$ Standing performance, very energetic and owning the stage
What can I said.....If u ain't laughing U ain't livin!...It came on time and new as advertised, Very funny dude
I got this DVD fast. No complaints with Carlos Mencia. He still is just as funny - really enjoyed it.
When I got my movie it came quicker than what I expected. My husband was very happy with how quick the service was from start to finish. Thank you for doing such an excellent job!!

I don't get what all the hype is with this guy. Every joke is exactly the same or stolen from another comedian. You want to hear some great standup watch Kevin James don't sweat the small stuff or Daniel Tosh completely serious or anything by Chris Tucker

I love the standup comedy of Carlos Mencia, not only is he funny but he is intelligently funny, most of his jokes actually make sense and you can tell that alot of thought are put into them. This is not his best work or standup I have ever seen but Mencia not at his best is still better than any other comedian any day in my opinion. Do not buy this if you get offended easily or do not have a sense of humor, because is definitely not for the easily offended. Mencia makes fun of every race, even his own, as a matter of fact he probably makes more fun of his own people than anyone else, so do not buy this if racial and ethnic jokes offend you because he makes fun of every race. If you love comedy and enjoy laughing you will enjoy Mencia. I recommend this dvd to everyone and if you do not know who Mencia is I would recommend that you first check out his standup dvd titled not for the easily offended, that one will have you laughing nonstop. Remember like Carlos says, If you're not laughing you're not living.

Carlos has gone too far with this one.

I used to really like his way of thinking and the way he could get his points across to the audience.

However, he sunk way too low with some of his comments.

I threw it away so I wouldn't have it in my home.

If you like Dane Cook, this might be ok for you.

Being a father has not changed Carlos - much.  He still uses awful language, and apparently, so does his school aged son - and he is okay with it. It is hard to imagine the worlds most popular, equal-opportunity racist as a father. Watch your back, Carlos - your son sounds like he is gonna follow close in your footsteps! And I can't wait for a Carlos and Company, as you and your son trade barbs.........it would be awesome!
This is an awesome show! Its up to date and Carlos is really inspired, all the jokes flow really natural and easy, and it keeps you laughing out loud during the whole show!
This was a great video, however it has a lot of bad language and is not appropiate for young children
Joe Rogan has it all wrong. Carlos doesn't steal any more material than any other comedian. He's not Samsung, he can formulate his own ideas.

First thing that hits you is he lost LOTS of weight.

His comedy is now super-streamlined, he's cut out alot of extraneous wandering and the whole special feels like it flows better than most of his other past performances. Some people may mistakenly claim that he 'cleaned up' his act, but if they say that, they're not listening. Its still definitely full of adult language and situations, and he adds lots of silly in the mix.

The video mastering is pretty clear for a standard def DVD, but there are NO useful frills on the dvd after the show, tho.
Man I wish he would come out with another DVD!  Can't stop laughing at this one.  Definitely one of his best!
